          "items": false,
          "minItems": 14,
          "maxItems": 14,
          "description": "Required complete verification sequence for CT14 (Aggregate closure); must contain exactly 14 successful discharge records, one per node from CT14.N01 through CT14.N14 in source order, each satisfying its corresponding concrete node schema."
